{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "d8108699-132d-4fc1-a711-34276e5497fd",
    "name": "Practo CMS V2 — Part 1: Script Workflow API",
    "description": "Complete API collection for Practo Hub CMS V2 — Part 1 (Phases 1–3: Script Creation to Script Lock).\n\n⚠️ Part 1 covers ONLY the script workflow (Phases 1–3 of the full 7-phase CMS flow).\nPhases 4–7 (video production, final package, language packages) are Part 2/3 scope.\n\n## Base URL\n- Cloudflare HTTPS (session): https://rewards-starting-enemies-goto.trycloudflare.com\n- Direct IP (permanent):      http://164.52.204.34:5001\n\n⚠️ Cloudflare URL changes on server restart. Direct IP never changes.\n\n## MinIO (S3 File Storage)\n- Cloudflare HTTPS (session): https://gathering-popularity-rfc-action.trycloudflare.com\n- Direct IP (permanent):      http://164.52.204.34:9002\n\n## How to use\n1. Run the 'Login' request for the role you want to test\n2. Token is auto-saved to {{token}} — no manual copy needed\n3. All other requests use {{token}} automatically\n\n## Test Accounts (all use password: Admin@123)\n- Super Admin      → admin@practo.com\n- Medical Affairs  → medical@practo.com\n- Content/Brand    → brand@practo.com\n- Agency POC       → agency@practo.com\n- Content Approver → approver@practo.com\n\n## Seed Data (ready to test immediately)\n- Script ID: seed-script-001  (status: DRAFT)\n\n## Full Workflow Order (Part 1 — Phases 1 to 3)\n\nStep 0  [Medical Affairs]   POST /api/scripts                           → Create Script (title, insight, content — Title/Topic is one field)\nStep 1  [Medical Affairs]   POST /api/scripts/:id/submit               → DRAFT → CONTENT_BRAND_REVIEW\nStep 2a [Content/Brand]     POST /api/scripts/:id/reject               → CONTENT_BRAND_REVIEW → DRAFT (needs changes, Medical Affairs revises and re-submits)\nStep 2b [Content/Brand]     POST /api/scripts/:id/approve              → CONTENT_BRAND_REVIEW → AGENCY_PRODUCTION\nStep 3  [Agency POC]        POST /api/scripts/:id/submit-revision      → AGENCY_PRODUCTION → MEDICAL_REVIEW\nStep 4a [Medical Affairs]   POST /api/scripts/:id/reject               → MEDICAL_REVIEW → AGENCY_PRODUCTION (Agency revises and re-submits)\nStep 4b [Medical Affairs]   POST /api/scripts/:id/approve              → MEDICAL_REVIEW → CONTENT_BRAND_APPROVAL\nStep 5  [Content/Brand]     POST /api/scripts/:id/approve              → CONTENT_BRAND_APPROVAL → CONTENT_APPROVER_REVIEW\nStep 6  [Content Approver]  POST /api/scripts/:id/lock                 → CONTENT_APPROVER_REVIEW → LOCKED ✅\n\n🚨 Emergency only:\n        [Super Admin]       POST /api/scripts/:id/unlock               → LOCKED → CONTENT_APPROVER_REVIEW",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "53168836",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/50573890-d8108699-132d-4fc1-a711-34276e5497fd?source=collection_link"
  },
